title: Best Remixes of Popular Songs [May 2014] [2 Hours] [Dubstep] [Trap] [House] [EDM]
description: Hey guys, this is a longer mix of some remixes of popular songs in may 2014. Although some of these remixes are somewhat older, I cant believe how awesome they are, and i hope you think so as well. If you guys enjoy the mix, please remember to leave a like sometime during the video and maybe even subscribe for some more of your favorite mixes coming soon :) Within the next month or 2, ill be trying to upload quite more and maybe even daily videos eventually. A big thanks to all my fans for the support through all of my mixes. Peace out guys, and remember to keep livin that Music Life. ▼♫Song List♫▼ ♫Calvin Harris - Summer (Club Killers Festival Trap Remix) [0:00] ♫John Legend - All of Me (Kasum Remix) [3:26] ♫American Authors - Best Day of My Life(Just a Gent Remix)[7:33] ♫Lady Gaga - Applause (Viceroy Remix) [12:24] ♫Avicii - Hey Brother (Airzz Bootleg Remix) [16:48] ♫Steve Aoki - Boneless (Ookay Remix) [22:25] ♫Bruno Mars - Young Girls (PaulHard & Vendetta Remix) [24:03] ♫Calvin Harris - Summer (Bombs Away Remix) [29:02] ♫Christina Perri - Human (Modern Machines Remix) [33:49] ♫One Republic - Counting Stars (Thomas Jack Remix) [39:09] ♫Demi Lavato - Neon Lights (Belanger Remix) [46:32] ♫Iggy Azalea - Fancy (Mike Thomson Remix) [51:48] ♫Imagine Dragons - Demons (White Panda Remix) [55:27] ♫Jason Derulo - Wiggle (Mark Rowan Remix) [59:42] ♫John Newman - Love Me Again (Sound Remedy Remix) [1:03:22] ♫Naughty Boy - La La La (KAW Remix) [1:06:59] ♫Paramore - Still Into You (Topher Jones Remix) [1:11:07] ♫Pitbull ft.
